ession_costs.csv", "s3_uri": "s3://sana-kramabench/datagov/kramabench-wildfire-hard-4/files/nifc_suppression_costs.csv"}) [toolUseId=call_3kNIA4ZR4C4SpdGsAeD5aavz]
